"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_thirst_lua"										"Thirst[CHC]"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_thirst_lua_Description"							"Bloodseeker is invigorated by the wounds of his enemies <font color='#70EA72'> within a %radius% range</font> , restoring with each kill. It also boosts Bloodseeker's Movement Speed, which intensifies as the around enemy's lower HP. The bonus Movement Speed reaches its max when the enemy's HP falls below %max_threshold_pct%%. Unlocks max movement speed for Bloodseeker."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_thirst_lua_Lore"									"Strygwyr becomes frenzied when blood is spilled."
