"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_blood_mist_lua"										"Blood Mist[CHC]"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_blood_mist_lua_Description"							"Bloodseeker sprays his blood continuously in the area around him, losing health to damage his enemies. The radius of Blood Mist is equal to Bloodseeker's Movement Speed. Enemies at the edge of the Blood Mist take %damage% damage; for every %range_damage_threshold% units they move closer to Bloodseeker, the damage increases by %range_damage_pct%%%. <br>Requires learning <font color='#70EA72'>Thirst</font>."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_blood_mist_lua_Note0"									"Damage dealt to Bloodseeker is non-lethal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_bloodseeker_blood_mist_lua_damage"					"HP PER SECOND COST/DAMAGE:"
